Class MozFlexBasis

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.webfirmframework.wffweb.css.core.AbstractCssProperty<MozFlexBasis>
      • com.webfirmframework.wffweb.css.css3.MozFlexBasis
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CssProperty, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable
    public class MozFlexBasis
extends AbstractCssProperty<MozFlexBasis>
     -moz-flex-basis: length|auto|initial|inherit;

 The -moz-flex-basis property specifies the initial length of a flexible item.

 Note: If the element is not a flexible item, the -moz-flex-basis property has no effect.
 Default value:  auto
 Inherited:      no
 Animatable:     yes
 Version:        CSS3
 JavaScript syntax:      object.style.mozFlexBasis="200px"
    Since:
    1.0.0
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
